# Astro + Tailwind Patterns

## Component Structure

```astro
---
interface Props {
  title: string;
}
const { title } = Astro.props;
---
<section class="py-20">
  <h2 class="text-elegant-serif text-4xl">{title}</h2>
  <slot />
</section>
```

## Design Tokens

- **Colors:** `academy-pink` (#e298b4), `academy-dark` (#1a1a1a)
- **Fonts:** `font-serif` (Playfair Display), `font-sans` (Montserrat)
- **Custom classes:** `text-elegant-serif`, `text-modern-sans`, `btn-outline`, `floral-bg`, `card-dark-translucent`

## Tailwind Usage

- Prefer responsive: `md:grid-cols-2`, `md:text-8xl`
- Spacing: `py-20`, `px-6`, `gap-12`
- Avoid arbitrary values unless needed; use design tokens

## Layout

- Container: `container mx-auto px-6`
- Sections: `py-20` or `py-24`
- Grid: `grid md:grid-cols-2` or `md:grid-cols-3`
